{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everybody knows that vampires can transform into bats. Three of them even, in the case of Tricula - he's three squares tall, after all! What is less known about him is that his legs occasionally run off by themselves, or that his arms might have some trouble putting his head back on in the right orientation. But when they behave and work together, those three body parts can reach the stars!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/extras/showcase_bats.gif?t=1736374682\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Tricula the vampire and manipulate your surroundings in a way that lets you reach your coffin. Stack pillars, fly over pits, build stairs out of rubble, deconstruct and reconstruct yourself and your obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/extras/showcase_rubble.gif?t=1736374682\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This Demo contains 30 unique levels that will challenge you to master all of Tricula's abilities in order to conquer this grid-based 2D puzzle platformer world of his.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game was made using the Godot Engine.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736374682","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/page.bg.jpg?t=1736374682","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736374682","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414230/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736374682","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"